						<div class="postbody">There are 2 version of Micro Machines - one with 1991 on title screen (works better on PAL Famiclone, without any glitches, on NTSC there are minor glitches) and one with 1992 on title screen (works without any glitches on NTSC, hangs after codemasters logo on PAL).</div>

